E-01 ENTER DELIVERY CODE!                                               1
E-02 ENTER FACTORY CODE!                                                2
E-03 DATE IS INVALID!                                                   3
E-04 CONTAINER WEIGHT SHOULD NOT BE 0!                                  4
E-05 ENTER Y OR N!                                                      5
E-06 TARGET DATA NOT FOUND!                                             6
E-07 DELIVERY CODE DOES NOT EXIST IN PACKING LIST MASTER <AB#C90>!      7
M-08 FRS LIST SHOULD BE PRINTED...                                      8
E-09 BIN ERROR!                                                         9
E-10 PRINTER SELECTION ERROR!                                          10
E-11 USE FORD MENU!                                                    11
E-12 ORDER NOT FOUND!                                                  12
E-13 ENTER Y AT LEAST FOR ONE DOCUMENT!                                13
M-14 PRESS F5 TO PROCESS...                                            14
E-15 ENTER ORDER#. (BLANK ORDER# IS NOT ALLOWED FOR THIS CUSTOMER! )   15
E-16 ORDER# SHOULD BE BLANK! (THERE IS P/L WITH ORDER# BLANK)          16
